code: public void process(SearchHit hit) throws IOException {     jsonBuilder.startObject().     for (ExtractedField field : fields.getAllFields()) {         writeKeyValue(field.getAlias(), field.value(hit)).     }     jsonBuilder.endObject(). }

private void writeKeyValue(String key, Object... values) throws IOException {     if (values.length == 0) {         return.     }     if (values.length == 1) {         jsonBuilder.field(key, values[0]).     } else {         jsonBuilder.array(key, values).     } }
